Before running install file please install Dependencies
you must install aria2 bc pm-utils wget vorbis-tools
for debian base distributions :  debian , ubuntu , mint , ...
sudo apt-get install aria2 xclip  wget  pm-utils  bc vorbis-tools
for fedora:
sudo dnf install aria2  wget  xclip pm-utils  bc vorbis-tools
for arch:
sudo pacman -S aria2  wget xclip pm-utils  bc vorbis-tools
